headline: Fruitist Closes $150 Million in Funding Led by J.P. Morgan Asset Management to Power Global Expansion and Meet Surging Demand for Healthy Snacking
summary: LOS ANGELES, October 29, 2025--Fruitist, the global superfruit brand inspiring the world to snack healthier, today announced it has closed $150 million in equity financing led by a vehicle managed by J.P. Morgan Asset Management, alongside other new and existing investors.
